{"type": "article", "id": 28481, "title": "同时盛热饮冷饮的保温杯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-21T06:46:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702160403PleOcSqQ0HiMB5N4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>市面上现有的保温杯往往只有一种功能，如果想同时带热饮冷饮只能多带一个杯子，今天介绍的这款名为 Golchi 的多功能保温杯则打破了这种尴尬的局面。它采用模块化的设计，上下两部分的隔层可以用来存放药品或者饮料冲剂等干燥的物品，清洁时也可以拆开支持机洗。针对不同温度的饮料，杯口还设计成三段式的构造，比如在喝热咖啡的时候可以轻轻地推开滑块，大口喝水的时候就可以推到第三段畅饮了。如果你对这个保温杯感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1527883519/golchi-worlds-most-versatile-and-customizable-bott\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 32 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160400UVi9Q7Xd4THbeMvt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55817378\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160401FC36a1XsVGt4bcmg.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160402KkuahtTf29qQZPCz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66273932\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160403VpH8IKZ0tANvwBGQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}